{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_07_01",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏の新曲完成後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "新曲用の衣装、見ましたよ。凄く良かったです\nさすがはfranさんがデザインしただけはありますね",
      "startTime": 6.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふん、当たり前じゃないですか\n私、自分のファッションブランドを持ってたんですよ？",
      "startTime": 12.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "そのブランド、『ERFOLG』のアイテムだって\n自分自身でデザインしていたんですから",
      "startTime": 19.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、今回は制作をかなり自由に\nやらせてもらえたから、特に自信があるんですけど",
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "あくまでアイドルの範囲内で大人の色気を出すことで\n他のアイドルとの差別化を図りましたし",
      "startTime": 33.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "素材や加工も細かく指示して、水着を模したものでも\n安っぽく見えないよう、立体感が出るようにしたんです",
      "startTime": 40.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……三人それぞれのスタイルに合わせて\nディティールを考えるのも、楽しかったですね",
      "startTime": 48.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "……ただ、それを着るのがmihoとkanaだって\n思うと、ちょっと癪なんですけどね",
      "startTime": 54.5333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど、相当こだわり抜いたんですね\nあのクオリティも納得です。ただ……",
      "startTime": 62.4000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "……？　なんですか？\n言いたいことがあるならはっきり言って下さいよ",
      "startTime": 69.5666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ええとですね……こだわりは本当に素晴らしいことだと\n思うんですが、予算をだいぶオーバーしてしまっていて",
      "startTime": 77.0301371415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "そ……それはしょうがないでしょ！？\n作るなら魂を込めて全力でこだわらないと！",
      "startTime": 84.5666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、衣装一つにもこだわり抜いた方が\n結果的にスリクスの評判に繋がるでしょ？",
      "startTime": 91.6666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "だから、これは必要な出費……\nううん、むしろ投資よ、投資！",
      "startTime": 97.6000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "な、なるほど。MV撮影の費用、大丈夫かなぁ……\nとにかく一度、残りの予算内でやりくりしてみます",
      "startTime": 106.2666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（とは言ったものの……本当に大丈夫だろうか）\n（もう九割近く使っちゃってるんだよな……）",
      "startTime": 115.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "startTime": 119.8748081684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night",
      "startTime": 120.9333351135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "MV撮影のスケジュール、決まりました？\n衣装の見せ方とか相談したいんですけど",
      "startTime": 125.2333351135,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 121.3666684468
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんですが……すみません……\n予算的に、なんともならなくてですね……",
      "startTime": 132.1666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　ちょ、ちょっと、どういうこと？\nなんとかするって言ったじゃない",
      "startTime": 139.1000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "手は尽くしたんですが、監督やカメラマンさんに\n依頼する費用さえもない状況でして……",
      "startTime": 144.2000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "まさか、私が衣装にお金をかけ過ぎたって言いたいん\nですか！？　あれは必要な投資だって言いましたよね！",
      "startTime": 151.8000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それはいいんです。ただ、みなさんがルームサービスを\nだいぶ自由に使っていたのが響いていまして",
      "startTime": 159.8000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ああいった費用も予算の内ですから。それに\n今回の件については三枝さんも渋い顔をしてるんです",
      "startTime": 167.0000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうせ一番贅沢しまくったのはkanaでしょ？\n私はそこまで……",
      "startTime": 175.2666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "あ、いや……確かに「いいアイデアを出すためには\n優雅な休憩も必要」って思って",
      "startTime": 183.4333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "シャンパンを開けはしたけど……\nそういえばあれって、結構高かったっけ……",
      "startTime": 190.9666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんによると、上機嫌に酔ったfranさんが\n北京ダックを受け取っていたと……",
      "startTime": 198.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "うっ……そ、それは……\n確かに、シャンパンを飲んで気分が良くなってきて……",
      "startTime": 204.6666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "気付いたら……\n机の上に、空のお皿が置いてあったけど……",
      "startTime": 210.9333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "酔っぱらってる間に注文してしまったんですね……",
      "startTime": 215.3666773956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "しょ、しょうがないでしょ！？\nていうか、酔ってたせいで味を覚えてないんだけど……",
      "startTime": 221.6333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、あの日は元々チートデイに設定してましたから\n多少食べ過ぎても全然問題ないですけどね",
      "startTime": 230.5666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor022.m4a",
      "text": "鴨肉は美容にもいいし、一緒に野菜の栄養もしっかり\n摂れてる……はず？　です",
      "startTime": 238.5666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-kor023.m4a",
      "text": "その……翌朝は頭がちょっとガンガンしてたので\nさすがに飲み過ぎたかなとは思うんですけど",
      "startTime": 249.1666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "franさんの美容意識の高さは知ってますし\nそこはいいんですが……やはり費用の方が……",
      "startTime": 256.5333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_07_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさんがエステティシャンから聞いたらしいん\nですが……エステサービスも受けてましたよね？",
      "startTime": 264.5000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
